data.description: Don’t miss the opportunity to own this beautiful three-bedroom ranch home on a large lot in Lakewood Park. This home has been well-maintained throughout the years and has huge potential with the upstairs walk-in attic. Adding some drywall and floors to the permanent attic space will make this home and sqft space double. Spend lovely summer nights and cozy winters in your four season sunroom over looking your private backyard and garden space. 2013 Roof and new Water Heater to give you extra bonus of piece of mind. Located by military bases, I-64, shopping and restaurants and Riverview Park and Menchville Marina.
